# HTTP request examples for my-service
# Compatible with VS Code REST Client and JetBrains HTTP Client.
# Start the server first: make dev

@base = http://localhost:8000

### Health check (liveness probe)
GET {{base}}/health

### Readiness check (readiness probe)
GET {{base}}/ready

### List all items
GET {{base}}/api/v1/items/

### Create an item
POST {{base}}/api/v1/items/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Widget",
  "description": "My first item"
}

### Create an item (no description)
POST {{base}}/api/v1/items/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bare item"
}

### Get item by ID (replace 1 with the id returned above)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/items/1

### Get a non-existent item (expect 404)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/items/999
